---
import Leaderboard from "./Leaderboard.svelte";
---

<div class="flex items-center justify-center">
  <div
    class="flex flew-row justify-center p-6 gap-8 w-full font-mono items-start max-lg:flex-col max-lg:items-center"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center max-w-xl gap-4 shrink-0">
      <h1 class="text-bg-100 font-bold text-3xl mb-6 max-lg:mb-3">
        The Playtime Leaderboard for Pomomon Farm
      </h1>

      <p class="text-bg-200 text-lg text-left max-lg:hidden">
        The Pomomon Club Leaderboard Standard is an API specification that
        allows anyone to implement the Pomomon Farm Playtime Leaderboard in
        their version of the game. The leaderboard updates in real time, in
        fact, you may be able to see it update right here on this page.
      </p>

      <p class="text-bg-200 text-lg text-justify mb-8 max-lg:hidden">
        The standard and implementation is not yet complete and still in early
        stages. Things may change and are not final yet. However, a draft of the
        first version of the standard is available in the navigation bar.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="text-bg-200 text-lg text-justify max-w-xl hidden max-lg:block">
      The Pomomon Club Leaderboard Standard is an API specification that allows
      anyone to implement the Pomomon Farm Playtime Leaderboard in their version
      of the game. The leaderboard updates in real time, in fact, you may be
      able to see it update right here on this page.
    </p>

    <div class="grow w-full max-w-xl">
      <Leaderboard client:only="svelte" />
    </div>

    <p
      class="text-bg-200 text-lg text-justify max-w-xl mb-8 hidden max-lg:block"
    >
      The standard and implementation is not yet complete and still in early
      stages. Things may change and are not final yet. However, a draft of the
      first version of the standard is available in the navigation bar.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
